Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜裡 在不經意間聞到花香時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就感到仿佛要想起什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 又總是想不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那似是令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又似是令人恐懼的某種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.66,title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2500,0)\p1\c&H49F4ED&\pos(235,500)}m 0 0 l -500 0 l -500 100 l 0 100
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.66,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(2500,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\fs65\pos(222,83)}散發芳香的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是個旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這雨太大 我沒法趕路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便讓我借宿一晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來歇著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你是蟲師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果碰上了什麼怪事或是身體有不舒服的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不定能幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不知道啊 我們全家的長處就是身體好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說頭疼的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是天天幹活沒得偷閒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你是旅行者 那就說說其他地方的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經很久沒離開過這個村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能聽到那麼多不尋常的事 我也覺得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們過得都很平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安無事是最好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都這麼晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快點回去 要不她會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花的香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又感覺自己像是忘記了什麼重要的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這地方以前有這個洞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有人挖的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花香…是從這裡傳出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這裡是不是會通往別的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個方向說不定是回村的近道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺要被花香悶得喘不過氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底忘記了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 記得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久 很久之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行 你們差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口碑不是都一年不如一年了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我加工錢就釀出更好的酒來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 現在的工錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還敢頂嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 把那個撿一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙搞什麼嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還撒謊！薰都說他看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 一句道歉都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就給我滾出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都漏光了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰 該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 那女孩好像在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 她究竟是誰來著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才 突然有一種十分懷念的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幫你背
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 好像有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 到底是哪裡不對勁…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了 又想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 這個洞我以前也見過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花香…是從這裡傳出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這裡應該能通往別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不她會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又好像快要想起什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經想不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這段時間總覺得不太對頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直住在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻常常有種十分懷念的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行 你們差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣的事之前也發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…是那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 她是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個情景我也見過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在很久 很久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 很久之前究竟是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是 無論如何也想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是個旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這雨太大 我沒法趕路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便讓我借宿一晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你是蟲師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果碰上了什麼怪事或是身體有不舒服的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不定能幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不知道啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你是叫銀古吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 我心裡一直有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打從我記事起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就常常覺得應該是第一次發生的事曾經見過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得同樣的事以前也發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在…也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也讓你在這樣的雨夜留宿過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我這是頭一次到這附近來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這倒也沒什麼影響
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是總覺得心神不寧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道這種事是不是本來就偶爾會發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既視感…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會不會是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚聞到花香就覺得不安？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像忘記了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你或許是被「迴陋」給困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是一種會散發出花香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引昆蟲或者野獸進入的黑筒狀的蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 據說這種蟲會將被引入的獵物的時間扭曲成環狀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獵物就會重覆地活在同一段時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重覆…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人有辦法確認是不是確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果真是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你應該已經經歷過許多次同樣的人生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且 之後你還會再碰上迴陋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你對此沒有意識 再一次走了進去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼時間就會重來 你又會經歷同樣的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然記錄上能找到擁有既視感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但畢竟無法做徹底的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得知那個人人生的每個細節是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在…重覆同樣的事…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒法斷定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你最好小心會發出花香的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被迴陋困住的人隨心所欲地改變了過去的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 擁有了既視感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許也就意味著你無法和以前一樣回到過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果穿行的次數太多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能會在不知不覺間和迴陋同化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千萬別再往裡鑽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我的確有想要改變的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我更想看到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如長大成人的女兒 孫子的小臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有那些從未見過的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 郁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去摘野菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都這麼晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好幾次鑽進了這個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後回到了過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回來得這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個你是我從來沒見到過的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像…一直在做著幸福的惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼呢 究竟怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都會是新的一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 郁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郁…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅持一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就帶你去找大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郁的身體在漸漸冷下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這麼下去 不等回村就要——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千萬別再往裡鑽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…聽我說 郁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個洞裡傳出了花香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是回村的近道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後又會在遙遠的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起生活的……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才 好像快想起什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郁 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟…是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像 既讓人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又讓人恐懼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是個旅行者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這雨太大 我沒法趕路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便讓我借宿一晚嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 殘紅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
